                <div class="card-img-top overflow-hidden gradient-overlay"><img src="/content/img/photo/photo-1484154218962-a197022b5858.jpg" alt="Modern, Well-Appointed Room" class="img-fluid"><a class="tile-link" href="detail-rooms"></a>
